  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODFkNmUzMjZkODUyYzEyMWQ0ZDJkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0zMDQmaGVpZ2h0PTMyMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/81d6e326d852c121d4d2d.jpg?width=304&amp;height=320\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/81d6e326d852c121d4d2d.jpg?width=304&amp;height=320\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/81d6e326d852c121d4d2d.jpg?width=304&amp;height=320\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>內地社交媒體「小紅書」，昨日有用戶「螞蟻仔」貼出一段影片，顯示有警員在旺角警署外，協助一名內地遊客，撿回跌進雨水渠的證件。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>三名警員動用工具之餘更直接把手伸進渠內，最後成功撿回。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmRhNTc2MTExYjMzYzlkZjhhYzJkLmpwZz93aWR0aD01MjEmaGVpZ2h0PTgwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fda576111b33c9df8ac2d.jpg?width=521&amp;height=800\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fda576111b33c9df8ac2d.jpg?width=521&amp;height=800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fda576111b33c9df8ac2d.jpg?width=521&amp;height=800\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>不過香港撐警籃私陣營「Save HK」皆認為是浪費警力。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>有香撐警之稱的籃私陣營</b><b>Facebook群</b><b>「Save HK」</b><b>不滿聲稱</b><b>「好心疼……香港警察有時真係好做唔做，真係慘囉」、「什麼事都找他们，做最多的事受最多的抹黑，很多港人沒良心」。組亦有轉發帖文，指前線警員工作已非常辛苦，應拒絕不合理的舉報，批評警區上級居然認同警員做這些工作，諷「下次屋企塞屎渠都要搵警察去幫手通渠」，有留言亦憂會引來更多「無謂call」。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>「Save HK」截圖</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGMxMDgyNGQ0YmM1MGM5YWFjYjg2LmpwZz93aWR0aD01MjMmaGVpZ2h0PTc5OQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc10824d4bc50c9aacb86.jpg?width=523&amp;height=799\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc10824d4bc50c9aacb86.jpg?width=523&amp;height=799\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc10824d4bc50c9aacb86.jpg?width=523&amp;height=799\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGI4ZjQxNWNkYjBkYTY5ZDM2OWE1LmpwZz93aWR0aD00NDQmaGVpZ2h0PTc5OQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/db8f415cdb0da69d369a5.jpg?width=444&amp;height=799\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/db8f415cdb0da69d369a5.jpg?width=444&amp;height=799\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/db8f415cdb0da69d369a5.jpg?width=444&amp;height=799\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b> </div>",
